(266, 1, '2013-03-19 15:18:00', '2013-03-19 15:18:00', 'Hello! My name is Jon Lewis and I am a professional Web Developer, musician, and photographer. I live in Toronto, Ontario, Canada, and graduated out of Fanshawe College in London, Ontario for Multimedia Design &amp; Production. This is my home for all of my online content, pretty much everything I''ve created and plan to create. I wanted to create a forum to showcase and discuss my work, so feel free to comment, share and contact me for anything! I am available for new projects and always looking for exciting new opportunities. Hope you enjoy the experience!\r\n\r\n-Jon', 'BIO', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-4', '', '', '2013-03-19 15:18:00', '2013-03-19 15:18:00', '', 4, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=266', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(267, 1, '2013-03-25 02:58:57', '2013-03-25 02:58:57', 'Hello! My name is Jon Lewis and I am a professional Web Developer, musician, and photographer. I live in Toronto, Ontario, Canada, and graduated out of Fanshawe College in London, Ontario for Multimedia Design &amp; Production. This is my home for all of my online content, pretty much everything I''ve created and plan to create. I wanted to create a forum to showcase and discuss my work, so feel free to comment, share and contact me for anything! I am available for new projects and always looking for exciting new opportunities. Hope you enjoy the experience!\r\n\r\n-Jon', 'BIO', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-5', '', '', '2013-03-25 02:58:57', '2013-03-25 02:58:57', '', 4, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=267', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(268, 1, '2013-03-25 02:17:53', '2013-03-25 02:17:53', 'Hi everyone! Welcome to my new online portfolio! It''s been long overdue, and delayed partly because of my indecisiveness on the design. I''ve submitted to my perfectionism and gone with a ThemeForest Template. I thought this one was pretty snazzy ;) In the end, it''s most important to get the content up, and I can basically do what I wan''t with this design going forward. Looking forward to keeping you guys updated!', 'Welcome to my new site!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '226-revision-3', '', '', '2013-03-25 02:17:53', '2013-03-25 02:17:53', '', 226, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=268', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(269, 1, '2013-03-25 03:11:41', '2013-03-25 03:11:41', 'I started doing Web Design in High School, and co-op''d at Apogee Recording Studio in Orono, Ontario. I designed websites for my band at the time, and many other bands in the area. (My other passion was music ;)) Back in those days, I was confined to Corel Draw and an early version of Adobe Photoshop. I can''t even remember what type of text editor I was using! Memories... Anyways, after excelling in Digital Communications in High School, I enrolled in Multimedia Design &amp; Production at Fanshawe College in London, Ontario, which is where I first learned proper HTML, CSS &amp; Javascript among other things, like Graphic Design, Video Production, Flash, 3D &amp; Sound Production. I decided to focus on Web Production after in graduated in 2005, and found contracts at Ontario Children''s Mental Health, and a few other various companies doing short-term contracts.\n\nAfter moving to Toronto, my career has taken me to such agencies as Digital Cement, <a href="http://thrillworks.ca/" target="_blank">Thrillworks</a>, Forge Media + Design, and now The Globe and Mail, where I''m currently enjoying working on their Globe Unlimited Subscription Service.', 'WEB', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '233-autosave', '', '', '2013-03-25 03:11:41', '2013-03-25 03:11:41', '', 233, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=269', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
