(275, 1, '2013-03-25 01:01:50', '2013-03-25 01:01:50', 'From 2001 to 2006 I played Bass in a band called Torsion. These were my formative years as a musician and we made some great music together. I''m in the process of remixing some of our demos as we speak and plan to make as much available online as possible. Stay tuned for updates!', 'Torsion', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '145-revision-4', '', '', '2013-03-25 01:01:50', '2013-03-25 01:01:50', '', 145, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=275', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
